      <title>瑞银称特朗普关税措施将令新兴市场进一步蒙受损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/emerging-markets-face-further-losses-on-trump-tariffs-ubs-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团表示，新兴市场股票和货币容易进一步下跌，因为近期的抛售尚未完全反映唐纳德·特朗普潜在关税带来的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/emerging-markets-face-further-losses-on-trump-tariffs-ubs-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 11:05:55 GMT</pubDate>
