    <item>
      <title>贝莱德首席执行官称创纪录的客户现金“仅仅是个开始”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/blackrock-s-fink-says-record-client-cash-is-just-the-beginning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 年度客户现金流入达到创纪录的 6,410 亿美元，凸显了该公司在股票和债券、指数和主动型基金以及日益快速增长且利润丰厚的私人资产市场的全球影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/blackrock-s-fink-says-record-client-cash-is-just-the-beginning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨内阁授权军方击落无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/scholz-s-cabinet-authorizes-military-to-shoot-unidentifed-drones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨的内阁通过了一项立法，授权德国武装部队击落涉嫌监视军事基地、工业设施和其他关键基础设施的不明无人机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/scholz-s-cabinet-authorizes-military-to-shoot-unidentifed-drones</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:53:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保加利亚组建内阁以结束政治僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bulgaria-moves-forward-with-cabinet-to-break-political-deadlock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚中右翼政党试图打破僵局，提议组建联合政府，为这个巴尔干国家提供通过有效多数解决腐败和采用欧元等问题的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bulgaria-moves-forward-with-cabinet-to-break-political-deadlock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:24:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于供应风险，IEA 预计今年石油过剩将减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/oil-surplus-narrows-for-2025-amid-new-supply-risks-iea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署表示，由于需求强劲和供应面临新的风险，今年全球石油市场面临的过剩程度低于此前预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/oil-surplus-narrows-for-2025-amid-new-supply-risks-iea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
